import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Container,
  Typography,
  Button,
  Grid,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  CardMedia,
  AppBar,
  Toolbar,
  IconButton,
  Avatar,
  Paper,
} from '@mui/material';
import {
  ArrowForward,
  Notifications,
  Settings,
  Menu as MenuIcon,
  TrendingUp,
  AccountBalance,
  ShowChart,
} from '@mui/icons-material';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';

const HomePage: React.FC = () => {
  const navigate = useNavigate();

  return (
    <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
      <AppBar position="static" color="transparent" elevation={0}>
        <Toolbar>
          <IconButton
            size="large"
            edge="start"
            color="inherit"
            aria-label="menu"
            sx={{ mr: 2 }}
          >
            <MenuIcon />
          </IconButton>
          <Typography variant="h6" component="div" sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
            TD AMERITRADE
          </Typography>
          <IconButton color="inherit">
            <Notifications />
          </IconButton>
          <IconButton color="inherit">
            <Settings />
          </IconButton>
          <Avatar sx={{ ml: 2, bgcolor: 'primary.main' }}>JD</Avatar>
        </Toolbar>
      </AppBar>

      {/* Hero Section with Tree Background */}
      <Box
        sx={{
          position: 'relative',
          color: 'white',
          py: 12,
          overflow: 'hidden',
          '&::before': {
            content: '""',
            position: 'absolute',
            top: 0,
            left: 0,
            right: 0,
            bottom: 0,
            background: 'linear-gradient(rgba(11, 31, 26, 0.9), rgba(11, 31, 26, 0.9)), url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511497584788-876760111969?ixlib=rb-4.0.3")',
            backgroundSize: 'cover',
            backgroundPosition: 'center',
            zIndex: -1,
          },
        }}
      >
        <Container maxWidth="xl">
          <Grid container spacing={4} alignItems="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
              <Typography variant="h2" component="h1" gutterBottom sx={{ fontWeight: 700 }}>
                Trade with Confidence
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ mb: 4, opacity: 0.9 }}>
                Advanced trading tools and expert insights to help you navigate the markets
              </Typography>
              <Button
                variant="contained"
                color="secondary"
                size="large"
                endIcon={<ArrowForward />}
                onClick={() => navigate('/legend')}
                sx={{ px: 4, py: 1.5 }}
              >
                Start Trading
              </Button>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
              <Box
                component="img"
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611974789855-9c2a0a7236a3?ixlib=rb-4.0.3"
                alt="Trading Platform"
                sx={{
                  width: '100%',
                  height: 'auto',
                  borderRadius: 2,
                  boxShadow: 3,
                }}
              />
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </Box>

      {/* Features Section */}
      <Container maxWidth="xl" sx={{ py: 8 }}>
        <Typography variant="h3" align="center" gutterBottom>
          Powerful Trading Tools
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="h6" align="center" color="text.secondary" sx={{ mb: 6 }}>
          Everything you need to trade with confidence
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          {[
            {
              title: 'Advanced Trading',
              description: 'Professional-grade trading tools and real-time data',
              icon: <TrendingUp sx={{ fontSize: 40 }} />,
            },
            {
              title: 'Portfolio Management',
              description: 'Comprehensive tools to manage and optimize your investments',
              icon: <AccountBalance sx={{ fontSize: 40 }} />,
            },
            {
              title: 'Market Research',
              description: 'In-depth analysis and expert insights',
              icon: <ShowChart sx={{ fontSize: 40 }} />,
            },
          ].map((feature, index) => (
            <Grid item xs={12} md={4} key={index}>
              <Card sx={{ height: '100%', textAlign: 'center' }}>
                <CardContent>
                  <Box sx={{ color: 'secondary.main', mb: 2 }}>
                    {feature.icon}
                  </Box>
                  <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                    {feature.title}
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
                    {feature.description}
                  </Typography>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Grid>
          ))}
        </Grid>
      </Container>

      {/* Market Overview Section */}
      <Box sx={{ bgcolor: 'background.paper', py: 8 }}>
        <Container maxWidth="xl">
          <Typography variant="h3" align="center" gutterBottom>
            Market Overview
          </Typography>
          <Grid container spacing={3} sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
            {['S&P 500', 'NASDAQ', 'DOW', 'RUSSELL 2000'].map((index) => (
              <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3} key={index}>
                <Paper
                  elevation={0}
                  sx={{
                    p: 3,
                    bgcolor: 'background.default',
                    borderRadius: 2,
                    textAlign: 'center',
                  }}
                >
                  <Typography variant="subtitle2" color="text.secondary">
                    {index}
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="h6" color="secondary.main">
                    +1.23%
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                    4,783.45
                  </Typography>
                </Paper>
              </Grid>
            ))}
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </Box>

      {/* CTA Section */}
      <Box sx={{ py: 8 }}>
        <Container maxWidth="md">
          <Typography variant="h3" align="center" gutterBottom>
            Ready to Start Trading?
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="h6" align="center" color="text.secondary" sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
            Join millions of traders who trust TD Ameritrade
          </Typography>
          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', gap: 2 }}>
            <Button
              variant="contained"
              color="primary"
              size="large"
              onClick={() => navigate('/legend')}
              sx={{ px: 4, py: 1.5 }}
            >
              Open Account
            </Button>
            <Button
              variant="outlined"
              color="primary"
              size="large"
              sx={{ px: 4, py: 1.5 }}
            >
              Learn More
            </Button>
          </Box>
        </Container>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default HomePage;
